Class GSE2_0_Bulletin

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class GSE2_0_Bulletin
extends GSE2_1
    This class aids in parsing data in GSE2.0 bulletin format. It extends the GSE2_1 class to delegate all of the QuakeML generation.
